data.description: Location and convenience make this home a must see! It boasts 3 bedrooms and 1 and 1/2 baths all on one level. Fenced in area of the back yard for your fur babies. Ample sized front porch for your morning coffee. This quiet and established neighborhood is just a few quick steps from high school and just a couple minutes' drive to shopping, restaurants and I75. This one you don't want to miss so schedule your showing today!
